OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and sunny for most with
OL,6,Flight winds. Feeling humid as extreme
OL,7,Fheat builds across England and Wales.
OL,8,FCloudier and cooler for northwest
OL,9,FScotland with a little drizzle at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in the northwest,
OL,13,Fperhaps with some patchy rain for
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland and western Scotland.
OL,15,FLargely clear elsewhere but staying
OL,16,Fvery warm and muggy overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
